{"tid":2239000,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鬥法庭，摘假髮 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-10-11T14:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T14:32:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d5abdef1589de08c4f98499812c0feca5c81e5","tid":2239000,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201011/JAMY3Q6QUBBQBAB7QBJ7GNJZAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201011%2FJAMY3Q6QUBBQBAB7QBJ7GNJZAU%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=2e519b50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201011%2FJAMY3Q6QUBBQBAB7QBJ7GNJZAU%2F&h=06b65826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201011/JAMY3Q6QUBBQBAB7QBJ7GNJZAU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鬥法庭，摘假髮 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c9FN1xEtMUE_lPvSt2gdQG5mKTs=/1230x751/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CQBV66WLPBBY3ATWY2OCMWVDBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc9FN1xEtMUE_lPvSt2gdQG5mKTs%3D%2F1230x751%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCQBV66WLPBBY3ATWY2OCMWVDBE.jpg&h=51f60199&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員周浩鼎、葛珮帆藉一封匿名信批鬥法庭，吹響了中共指揮香港法庭的號角；另一議員何君堯更總結中共意旨，傳語同僚：「改革司法界，從摘下司法界的假髮開始。」<br />\n<br />\n香港司法界秉承英治時期傳統，法官與大律師上庭，都戴白色假髮，也許是象徵老成持重。一九九七年香港易手，終審法庭首席法官李國能曾咨詢司法界意見，最後還是決定不棄假髮，其中自有深意，不只是象徵而已。<br />\n<br />\n《荀子．哀公》載，魯哀公曾問孔子：「紳委章甫（衣冠偉然），有益於仁乎？」孔子怫然作色說：「君胡然也（主公怎麼了）？。。。。。。。。。。。。。。所說道理差不多。<br />\n<br />\n中共無疑也明白「紳委章甫，有益於仁」，所以，周浩鼎、何君堯這兩個新香港律師，現在摩拳擦掌，誓要先摘下司法界的假髮。"}]}